Additionally, it could be classified under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) because of the use of deep learning techniques. The paper could also be classified under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) because of the use of neural networks. Finally, it could be classified under multimedia (cs.MM) because it deals with medical image analysis.
